{"tid":1590262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人有粗口潔癖","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T16:16:37.000Z","uid":315761,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"80ebeed8517ae2edac6178c6600dad779d5d6e42","tid":1590262,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"我屋企人平日睇開cctvb，扮晒中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日我睇到個黑警講yellow object忍唔住講左句'正仆街'<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆即刻發晒癲嚟罵我，內容概述如下:<br />\n我唔理佢做過D咩，總之你講粗口就係唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！就係無修養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，無文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！無論你有幾唔鍾意佢都要尊重佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！你如果係大學(小弟讀hku)講粗口d人會點睇你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！咩形象都無呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n我心諗:大學生個個都講粗口&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老豆見我不為所動，就更加嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兼玩人身攻擊:你咁得閒講粗口，不如搞掂自己d功課同間房先&hellip;&hellip;你自己都搞唔掂自己憑乜講粗口呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n我心諗:<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26ead34b1f309311c3d8fe96388dc2a50c3fee7","tid":1590262,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"3ea7280ffb86adbf2597c4ae86c1b96515b62328","tid":1590262,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"叫佢畀黑警亂棍打兩嘢，再係新屋嶺坐48個鐘佢就明㗎喇"},{"pid":"45861c752c960cb9ecb53522c4554755859d498f","tid":1590262,"uid":56138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"起碼都要去到屌人老母先叫粗口呀<br />\n仆街呢啲咁都當粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801223d718eee2cfbcc3d9ee70ffbff47cec833f","tid":1590262,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45861c752c960cb9ecb53522c4554755859d498f","tid":1590262,"uid":56138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"起碼都要去到屌人老母先叫粗口呀<br />\n仆街呢啲咁都當粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"我屋企人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過講毅進仔都屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6c1b49a756e13f1e3b1781a064c0e55784574c","tid":1590262,"uid":15454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"要分唔同層次<br />\n你屌佢老母 <br />\n以後佢就會接受你句仆街"},{"pid":"21a678e7c4e61745678c9a57b5e1a5402514e41f","tid":1590262,"uid":241657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"日日講，講到你老豆咪撚再咁偽善"},{"pid":"8809f34153604a988845727139d4476c6a8b3dee","tid":1590262,"uid":215734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abNQYGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/